	"description"		"[h1]Enlisted - Military Service Mod[/h1]

[i]Enlist with any lord. Follow orders. Climb the ranks. Retire with honor.[/i]

Transform Bannerlord from a conquest simulator into a deep soldier career experience. Instead of managing an empire, you serve one. Features [b]245 narrative content pieces[/b] spanning [b]9 military ranks[/b] from fresh recruit to senior commander.

[b]Links:[/b] [url=https://github.com/Arkpointt/Enlisted]GitHub (Open Source)[/url] | [url=https://discord.gg/your-discord]Discord[/url]

════════════════════════════════════════════════

[h1]Key Features[/h1]

[h2]Military Career Progression[/h2]
[list]
[*][b]9 Military Ranks (T1-T9):[/b] Climb from recruit to marshal with culture-specific titles (Empire, Vlandia, Sturgia, Khuzait, Battania, Aserai)
[*][b]Multi-Factor Promotions:[/b] XP, service time, battles fought, reputation, and discipline all matter
[*][b]Narrative Proving Events:[/b] Key promotions trigger story moments that define your character
[*][b]Formation Choice:[/b] Pick your battlefield role (Infantry, Archer, Cavalry, Horse Archer)
[/list]

[h2]Chain of Command[/h2]
[list]
[*][b]16 Military Orders:[/b] Receive explicit directives from sergeants, lieutenants, and your lord
[*][b]85 Order Events:[/b] Dynamic encounters during duty execution (15-35% trigger chance per phase)
[*][b]Tiered Duties:[/b] T1-T3 auto-assigned basics, T4+ optional advancement missions
[*][b]Real Consequences:[/b] Success builds reputation, failure damages it. Decline too many orders = discharge
[/list]

[h2]Pay & Muster System[/h2]
[list]
[*][b]12-Day Pay Cycle:[/b] Wages accrue daily in muster ledger, paid ceremonially
[*][b]8-Stage Muster Ceremonies:[/b] Immersive pay events with baggage checks, inspections, promotions
[*][b]Pay Tension:[/b] When pay is late, tension rises and unlocks special choices
[*][b]Performance Modifiers:[/b] Bonuses for excellence, deductions for infractions
[/list]

[h2]Equipment & Quartermaster[/h2]
[list]
[*][b]6 Quality Tiers:[/b] Shoddy to Standard to Serviceable to Fine to Masterwork to Legendary
[*][b]Equipment Upgrades:[/b] Sequential quality improvements with real stat bonuses
[*][b]Reputation Discounts:[/b] 0-30% price reduction based on Soldier reputation
[*][b]Officers Armory (T7+):[/b] Elite gear catalog for commanders
[*][b]Provisions Shop (T7+):[/b] Premium rations with morale/fatigue boosts
[/list]

[h2]Camp Life Simulation[/h2]
[list]
[*][b]Background Simulation:[/b] Soldiers get sick, injured, desert. Equipment breaks. Morale shifts
[*][b]33 Player Decisions:[/b] Training, social, economic, recovery, medical, career activities
[*][b]Fatigue System:[/b] Actions accumulate fatigue, affecting performance and outcomes
[*][b]Medical Care:[/b] 15 injury types with 4 treatment options (surgeon, herbal, rest, emergency)
[/list]

